text: I studied the pictures for more than 3 minutes. Unfortunately, I could not discern specific properties that uniquely pertained to the species.
Just that I wish I could have been more help. There's nothing I could see that stands out as definitively describing the species.
I tried looking for patterns to no avail.
I am going to have to make guesses, so that's my only other advice: just try your best.
If you make sense of these creatures then you have succeeded where I could not.
